To modify a translation:

1) If necessary, copy the original translation file, for instance:
{{{
cp contrib/admin/locale/fr/LC_MESSAGES/django.po locale/fr/LC_MESSAGES
}}}

2) Change the translation in the django.po file

3) Generate the binary translation file:
{{{
msgfmt django.po --output-file django.mo
}}}

4) Commit the result to the repository
